  "title": "Accounts & Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative and accounts support to Seniors, including reconciliation of sales and purchase invoices against accounting software, credit card platforms, and bank statements</li><li>Prepare payment advice and supporting documents as requested by clients</li><li>Assist in preparing and issuing sales invoices using Xero/bookkeeping accounting software</li><li>Follow up on trade receivables and outstanding payments</li><li>Attend to incoming phone calls and basic client enquiries</li><li>Provide administrative support at client sites when required</li><li>Handle general administrative and ad-hoc tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Basic knowledge of accounting</li><li>Relevant administrative experience</li><li>Willing to learn, training will be provided</li></ul>",
